title: English Grammar in Use - Supplementary Exercises (2014)
description:
English Grammar in Use - Supplementary Exercises

With answers

(To accompany English Grammar in Use Fourth Edition)

Louise Hashemi  with  Raymond Murphy 

3th printing 2014

ISBN  978-1-107-61641-7




In 2015 the Cambridge and IELTS exams have been updated, and there are
many new books available for those exams.

Please, if you have a copy of a recent book, share it !!!

Scan the book, create a .Pdf file with Adobe Acrobat Pro for example,
and upload it.

Sharing is caring


enjoy!
